{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/01-26-who-influences-you"},"topicSectionsStyle":"detailedGrid","kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow","doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/Archive","doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/2015"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"date: 2015-01-26T22:08:35-06:00","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"I think it’s good to take a few minutes every once in a while and figure out who you are allowing to shape your life. As highly social creatures, we readily pick up on thoughts and habits in our environment that we may not notice in our daily lives. Fortunately, many of us have control over that environment — we can choose who we are around (both digitally and in the physical world), what we read, and the television we watch."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"I explicitly choose not to let cable news have an influence on me because I don’t want it shaping who I am. I do the same with people that seem to constantly complain on Twitter, “high drama” friends that always need attention, and reality TV."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Instead, I read and listen to "},{"identifier":"http:\/\/sethgodin.typepad.com","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"http:\/\/www.merlinmann.com","isActive":true},{"text":" (although he can be complain-y at times at which point I have to take some time away), ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"http:\/\/joelonsoftware.com","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"http:\/\/www.stevenpressfield.com","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"http:\/\/danbenjamin.com"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"http:\/\/shawnblanc.net","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"identifier":"http:\/\/www.asymco.com","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". I spend time with my girlfriend, close friends that provide support and that I can support, and my daughter. I try to surround myself with as much positive energy as possible."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you haven’t in a while, think about who and what is influencing you. Consider whether you need to do some pruning.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Brunow"}],"title":"Who Influences You","color":{"standardColorIdentifier":"purple"},"platforms":[{"name":"Brunow","introducedAt":"2017.01.20"}]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/brunow\/01-26-who-influences-you"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow/2015":{"title":"2015","identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/2015","abstract":[],"kind":"article","role":"collectionGroup","url":"\/documentation\/brunow\/2015","type":"topic"},"http://joelonsoftware.com":{"titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Joel Spolsky"}],"title":"Joel Spolsky","type":"link","identifier":"http:\/\/joelonsoftware.com","url":"http:\/\/joelonsoftware.com"},"http://shawnblanc.net":{"title":"Shawn Blanc","url":"http:\/\/shawnblanc.net","identifier":"http:\/\/shawnblanc.net","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Shawn Blanc"}],"type":"link"},"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow":{"title":"Brunow","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/brunow","abstract":[{"text":"David Brunow, known as Brunow [ˈbɹunoʊ] to the folks he works with, is a human living on Earth. You might have something in common with him — if you think it is ridiculous that he is talking about himself in the first person here, so does he.","type":"text"}],"role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow","type":"topic"},"http://www.asymco.com":{"title":"Horace Dediu","type":"link","identifier":"http:\/\/www.asymco.com","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Horace Dediu"}],"url":"http:\/\/www.asymco.com"},"http://www.merlinmann.com":{"title":"Merlin Mann","url":"http:\/\/www.merlinmann.com","identifier":"http:\/\/www.merlinmann.com","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Merlin Mann"}],"type":"link"},"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow/Archive":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/Archive","title":"Archive","kind":"article","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"All posts"}],"url":"\/documentation\/brunow\/archive","role":"collectionGroup","type":"topic"},"http://sethgodin.typepad.com":{"title":"Seth Godin","type":"link","identifier":"http:\/\/sethgodin.typepad.com","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Seth Godin"}],"url":"http:\/\/sethgodin.typepad.com"},"http://www.stevenpressfield.com":{"title":"Steven Pressfield","url":"http:\/\/www.stevenpressfield.com","identifier":"http:\/\/www.stevenpressfield.com","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Steven Pressfield"}],"type":"link"},"http://danbenjamin.com":{"title":"Dan Benjamin","type":"link","identifier":"http:\/\/danbenjamin.com","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Dan Benjamin"}],"url":"http:\/\/danbenjamin.com"}}}